        <mxCell id="v_KwPKzVUrEVAUu6fwGb-65" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fillColor=#ffcccc;strokeColor=#36393d;" value="Functional Requirements:&lt;div&gt;1. Users should be able to login to their respective accounts&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Users can follow each other&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Users can upload posts in different formats&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Users can like and comment on posts&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Users are displayed posts from their followed accounts on their feed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Non-functional Requirements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. 100M daily users&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. 25M of daily posts&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. &amp;lt;=500 ms latency&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Availability &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt; Consistency&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Effective Feed Caching&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
